<article id="post-255" class="post-255 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-careers category-family category-general category-trains category-travel tag-radical-entertainment tag-year-in-review">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2003/01/2002-year-in-review/" rel="bookmark">2002, A Year in Review</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>&#8220;Another year, come and gone&#8221; it wasn&#8217;t. This has perhaps been the single most turbulent year of my life. I had the deep low of my father&#8217;s death, coupled with the meteoric high of participating with the CBC 50th Anniversary train. Many times I thought I was going to lose my sanity or even my job. Perseverence, not to mention blind faith, helps moves things forward. But I did live up to a few things last year (see [[2001, A Year in Review]]): I spent more time out of the office. Not really getting a life, but it&#8217;s a start.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2003/01/2002-year-in-review/#more-255" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;2002, A Year in Review&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2003/01/2002-year-in-review/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2003-01-01T11:45:45-07:00">1 January 2003</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/careers/" rel="category tag">Careers</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/family/" rel="category tag">Family</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/trains/" rel="category tag">Trains</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/travel/" rel="category tag">Travel</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/radical-entertainment/" rel="tag">Radical Entertainment</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/year-in-review/" rel="tag">year in review</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2003/01/2002-year-in-review/#respond">Leave a comment<span class="screen-reader-text"> on 2002, A Year in Review</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
